data.description: Welcome to this rare ranch style home nestled in Quincy Lake! Be welcomed by newer exterior paint, new driveway and porch, new roof and gutters! As you enter the home your bright office is on the left a French door entry, the sitting area/family room off of the entry is open to the dining area, great for family dinners! The kitchen and living room flow to the newer covered composite deck, perfect for entertaining! All new stainless steel appliances, the kitchen features granite counters, under cabinet lighting, large pantry, and an island! The gas fireplace in the living room features custom, newer, gorgeous marble surround, and a new fan! Plan your gatherings now, this two tiered, composite, partially covered deck features stylish railings, lighting, a fan, and views of the mountains to watch sunsets! Luxury main level living, private primary bedroom with adjacent 5 pc  bath and custom walk in closet, spacious secondary rooms, remodeled 3/4 bath with custom cabinetry, and a laundry closet with cabinets! Enter the basement from the open stairway, and find a full wet bar with bar top, shelving, lots of counter space, full living/dining or gaming area! The 4th bedroom here is set for guests, and another 3/4 bath! The large utility room houses a newer H2O heater, and a brand new Carrier HVAC system with a transferable warranty, and a new radon mitigation system has been installed! Perfect location, close to trails, parks, minutes from highway access, amenities, and mountains! Contact me for a private showing or come view with your agent today!
